I"‘<p>GitHub is a really useful tool for software development, particularly when collaborating with lots of folks, and a great thing to learn to use.</p>
<blockquote>
  <p>GitHub is a web-based hosting service for software development projects that use the Git version control system. GitHub offers free accounts for open source projects. As of May 2011, GitHub was the most popular open source code repository site. The site provides social networking functionality such as feeds, followers and the network graph to display how developers work on their versions of a repository. [<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GitHub">Wikipedia</a>]</p>
</blockquote>
